Notifications
=============

The Noomii notification system!


Usage
=====

To install:

script/generate notifications_migration
rake db:migrate

To create new events:

script/generate cool_event <name_of_event>

This will generate a class in app/models/cool_events, and a mailer view in app/views/notification_mailer.

To trigger events:

EventName.trigger :source => source_object

To subscribe/unsubscribe to events, emails:

user.subscribe_to_cool_event(EventName)
user.unsubscribe_from_cool_event(EventName)
user.subscribe_to_cool_email(EventName)
user.unsubscribe_from_cool_email(EventName)

To check subscription:

user.subscribed_to_cool_event?(EventName)
user.subscribed_to_cool_email?(EventName)

To customize conditions for checking whether a user is subscribed, override Event.subscribers (a protected method), in your event subclasses.

